This patch enables to use spanish voice on festival. If this voice is not installed, install it using the command:

```
apt-get install festvox-ellpc11k
```

To apply the patch file, go to the Player home dir and run:

```
patch -p1 < patch/festival/festival.patch
```

To use the spanish voice with player, add this line on the speech driver in the config file:

```
language "spanish"
```
